e module lookup plus fallback public-field retrieval.\n- Updated `build.gradle` to:\n  - add a `macroSupport` source set,\n  - include the support output on the test runtime classpath,\n  - pass the resolved test classpath into JVM and Native Image test runs.\n\nThis should reach the remaining `CompileTimeEval$QuoteScope` call sites via the public macro API during test execution rather than compile-time-only expansion. I did not compile or run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05db16ac799a99ce0169f882da1e24819cb4e828c6c3fc62c9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1721, "output": 768, "cacheRead": 50176, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 52665, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777894093559, "responseId": "resp_05db16ac799a99ce0169f882ce3e80819cb0c1155c28a8dbe8"}}
